## Phase 1 -- Authorization

`orchestrator.py` shows a consent screen before anything touches the target. Reads your input -- if not exactly YES it exits. If YES it creates the engagement directory, generates a unique engagement ID, and saves initial `state.json`.

This runs even in FULL-AUTO mode. Cannot be bypassed. Creates a documented record that you confirmed authorization before any module ran.

