## Accountability Architecture Summary

Every phase of R3D enforces human accountability:

```
Phase 1    Authorization gate -- documented consent before any action
Phase 6    Verifier -- LLM output validated by Python and NVD
Phase 9    Improvement engine -- human approves every KB change
All        Telemetry log -- every action timestamped, MITRE tagged
All        Engagement ID -- complete chain of custody, one run one ID
```

The AI executes at speed. The human decides at every gate.
That is not a design preference -- it is how R3D was engineered.